I have been coming here since they opened many years back and they were ALWAYS expensive, but recently their portions become smaller (ikan bilis lesser, chicken wing alot smaller)

Food quality also dropped from before, only giving 4 stars cause chilli nice

But price they remain the same, disappointing. On the bright side, the close much later now since not alot people buy from them anymore
